turns.content:
Sound good. I appreciate us getting to a structure that protects the pace your team needs while making the workload predictable on my side.

I’ll draft a short addendum today with:
- a 20-hour monthly flex block at a discounted, guaranteed monthly rate;
- my standard hourly rate for any overage;
- coverage for fast-turn mockups, presentation updates, banners, and comparable launch-support requests;
- internal tracking with a brief heads-up near the limit, rather than approvals for individual requests;
- no interruption for genuinely urgent launch work, with overages reconciled afterward;
- a quick priority reset only if a request becomes a separate, substantial project.

I’ll send it over shortly so we can put this behind us and focus on Q3.
